生成宽度/生成高度：FLUX生成的尺寸，应该为8的倍数。其中一项设为0的话会自动根据加载图片的宽高比计算出相应尺寸（不能两项同时为0）。似乎分辨率过高会导致结果变差
    Width/Height for Generation: the size in FLUX generation, should be a multiple of 8. If one of the dimensions is set to 0, it will be automatically calculated according to the aspect ratio of the loaded image (do not set both to 0). If the resolution is too high, it seems that the result will probably be worse.

    背景去除开关：去除加载图片的背景（可以在ImageAndMaskPreview节点中mask_color设置RGB值改变去除后的颜色）
    BG Remove On/Off: Remove the background of input image (you can change the color of the removed area by setting RGB value in ImageAndMaskPreview node)


    格数选择：4格为In-Context-LoRA原本结构，但其实2格也能用，可以节约显存并提高结果与提示词的一致性（避免每隔图片之间提示词污染）
    Panel Count Switch: 4-Panels for the original structure of In-Context-LoRA, but 2-Panels also works, saving VRAM and improving the adherence of prompt (avoid prompt contamination between each image of panel)


    间隔宽度：在结果中的四张图（或两张图）之间加入白色间隔，似乎加入这个间隔可以提升生成效果。如果不希望有间隔就把它设为0
    Spacing Width: Add white spacing between the four-panel (or two-panel) in the result image. It seems that adding this spacing can improve the result. If you don't want the spacing, set it to 0


    参考图位置：加载的参考图在重绘生成过程中所在的位置，似乎对生成结果有影响。如果选择2格模式，只有前两项有效
    REF IMG Position: The position of loaded reference image, it seems the postion affect the result of inpaint generration. If the 2-Panel is enabled, only the first two in the setting are valid


    共通/部位提示词：Portrait Photography LoRA的使用需要按照特定的提示词结构，工作流加入五个文本框分别输入全局共通提示词和左上角、右上角、左下角、右下角提示词，提示词将自动组合为Portrait Photography LoRA需要的结构，在“组合提示词预览”中可以预览
    Common/Part Prompt: The use of Portrait Photography LoRA needs to follow a specific prompt structure, the workflow uses 5 text boxes to enter global common prompt, top-left prompt, top-right prompt, bottom-left prompt and bottom-right prompt, the prompts will automatically be combined into the structure which Portrait Photography LoRA need. You can preview it in "Combined Prompt Preview"

加载角色参考图
    Load the character reference image

重绘生成开关：控制Flux生成的开关。应当在第二步全部设置完成、点击生成后对预览全都满意后再打开并继续生成
    Generation On/Off: Switch that controls Flux generation. You should keep it off when setting params in step 2 and click Queue Prompt to preview "Mask Preview" and "Combined Prompt Preview" in step 2. Be sure you satisfied with those previews and then turn the siwtch on for inpaint generation


    生成步数：如果不使用Turbo LoRA，建议20步以上，如果使用，推荐12步
    Steps: If the Turbo LoRA is disabled, more than 20 steps is recommended. if the Turbo LoRA is enabled, 12 steps is recommended


    Turbo LoRA：使用alimama的Turbo LoRA减少生成步数（一般只需要8步，但本工作流推荐12步），加速重绘过程。Turbo LoRA则应设置为1
    Turbo LoRA: Use alimama's Turbo LoRA to reduce the generation steps (typically only 8 is needed, but 12 is recommended for this workflow). The weight should be set to 1


    In-Context-LoRA：使用alibaba的In-Context-LoRA。本工作流应当使用Portrait Photography LoRA。但似乎对于Fill模型没有多少作用
    In-Context-LoRA: Use alibaba's In-Context-LoRA. Should use Portrait Photography LoRA for this workflow. But it seems useless with Fill model


    使用手动提示词：当此项关闭时，自动使用第二步“组合提示词预览”的文本进行生成。打开此项后，将使用第三步“手动提示词”内的文本进行生成
    Manual Prompt： When it is disabled, workflow will use the "Combined Prompt Preview" in step 2 to generate. If it is enabled, will use the "Manual Prompt" in step 3 to generate


    ReActor换脸：提高角色脸部一致性。不支持二次元动漫。仅对分割后图片有效。
    ReActor FaceSwap: Improve character face consistency. No use for anime face. Available for Result-Cropped images only


    切割宽度：工作流将把生成的4格（或2格）图片分割开。由于第2步加入了间隔，需要在切割时也按照一定宽度将间隔区域去除。由于生成的随机性，每次生成结果的实际间隔不一定相同，一般来说需要将本项数值设置得比第2步的“间隔宽度”更大才能保证间隔被切割得干净
    Cross Crop Width: This workflow will split the resulting 4-panel (or 2-panel) image into indivedual ones. Because of the spacing added in step 2, you need to remove the spacing area according to a certain width when split as well. Due to the random nature of the generation, the actual spacing of the results may not be the same each time, in general, you need to set this value larger than the “spacing width” in step 2 to ensure that the spacing is cut cleanly

nodes.title: 左上提示词 | TOP-LEFT Prompt

widgets_values:
FLUX图生图一致性角色工作流使用须知：
Instructions for use of i2i_consistence_character_FLUX workflow:


1. 使用前仔细阅读所有蓝色文本框内的说明。除文本框外，其它蓝色节点代表需要加载模型，检查模型是否加载正确
1. Read instructions in the blue note nodes carefully before use the workflow. Blue nodes other than the note nodes represent that they need to load a model, check if the model is loaded correctly.


2. 与使用inpaint模型相比，Fill模型能够更好保持人脸以及其它各种细节的一致性，但同时对提示词也更加敏感，更难控制。
    一般情况下工作流需要16G显存运行，由于目前没有GGUF版本的Fill模型，无法进一步降低显存使用。
2. Compared to using the inpaint model, the Fill model is better able to maintain consistency of human faces and various other details, but at the same time is more sensitive to prompt and harder to control.
    Generally this workflow requires 16G VRAM to run, and since there is currently no GGUF version of the Fill model, it is not possible to further reduce VRAM usage.


3. 一般情况下Fill模型能够很好保持人脸一致性，但如果不满意可以使用ReActor换脸增加人脸的一致性。你也可以使用其它换脸插件对生成结果进行处理以实现同样功能。
3. In most cases the Fill model is able to maintain good face consistency, but if you are not satisfied with it you can use the ReActor face swap to increase the consistency of the face. You can also apply other face swap node to the generated result to achieve the same function.


4. 某些功能的节点如果没有安装并且也不需要使用，比如背景去除，可以直接删除，不影响主要功能。
4. Some nodes with certain features that are not installed and not needed, such as background removal, can be removed without affecting the main functionality.
